What you need to know:  The Prefontaine Classic will provide the athletes with a perfect opportunity to race on the venue for the World Championships slated for July 15-24 in the same venue.Kipyegon, who trains in Kaptagat, Elgeyo Marakwet County, will be keen to win her first 1500m race in the Diamond League this season, after finishing second in the 3000m in the season-opening Doha leg behind Burundi's Francine Niyonsaba.